<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - AHNS project</title><meta name="description" content=""/><meta name="keywords" content=""/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Auckland Head &Neck Specialists</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / AHNS</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">I've been working with Auckland Head & Neck Specialists for a year or two now and was originally tasked with building their first website. They're a relatively new surgery to the Auckland area and have aspirations to be Auckland's foremost head and neck surgery. Unlike their competition they see online as a key channel to reach new customers.</p><p>Recently they asked me about what methods they could use to increase their search ranking results. We discussed the recent changes to Google's algorythms and came to the conclusion that creating a blog would be their best long-term strategy for achieving this. They want to cement their site as the go to source for information on head and neck conditions in New Zealand.</p><p>I rebuilt the old site in <a href="http://wordpress.org/" target="_blank">WordPress</a> and installed a superb theme that is both responsive and amazingly customisable. They're now in the process of preparing a range of blog entries as well as an accompanying AdWords campaign.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/ahns/image_01_lge.jpg"><div id="project_lg" class="project"><img src="/images/works/projects/ahns/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="AHNS home page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/ahns/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/ahns/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="AHNS detail 01"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/ahns/image_03_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/ahns/image_03_sml.jpg" alt="AHNS detail 02"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section><ul><li><a href="http://www.ahns.co.nz/" target="_blank">Visit Website</a></li></ul></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>